<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Don&apos;t know whether I agree that it&apos;s a vast improvement on Perdido Street Station - I think each have their own virtues. I think some could claim The <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Don't know whether I agree that it's a vast improvement on Perdido Street Station - I think each have their own virtues. I think some could claim The Scar is also overly long, badly structured, and many characters are "unlikeable" but many scenes are very compelling and the is no disputing that Mieville can write.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
